WEBVTT

00:00:02.938 --> 00:00:05.058
Shah Rukh Khan: The speaker
joining us today,

00:00:05.058 --> 00:00:09.988
has developed a technology 
that recognizes voice very well.

00:00:10.208 --> 00:00:11.618
Words may be in any language,

00:00:11.658 --> 00:00:15.128
it understands the meaning
by just listening to the voice.

00:00:15.128 --> 00:00:16.254
How?

00:00:16.968 --> 00:00:17.968
I will not tell you.

00:00:17.968 --> 00:00:19.374
Hear from the man himself,

00:00:19.374 --> 00:00:23.474
Umesh Sachdev, the engineer 
and innovator from Chennai,

00:00:23.814 --> 00:00:28.728
how we can make our lives much simpler,
with just the use of voice.

00:00:28.896 --> 00:00:32.886
Please welcome on stage, 
Mr. Umesh Sachdev.